rference\\\",\\\"Orbital Mechanics\\\",\\\"Newtonian Physics\\\"],\\\"offers\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Offer\\\",\\\"price\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"priceCurrency\\\":\\\"USD\\\",\\\"availability\\\":\\\"https://schema.org/InStock\\\"}}\",\"id\":\"schema-org\"}])</script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"min-h-full flex flex-col bg-[#0b1220] text-[#e2e8f0]\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"flex flex-col min-h-screen bg-[#f8fafc]\"><header class=\"fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 transition-all duration-300 \" style=\"background:#0b1221;backdrop-filter:blur(20px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(20px);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);opacity:0;transform:translateY(-80px)\"><nav class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 h-[76px] flex items-center justify-between gap-4\"><a class=\"flex items-center shrink-0\" href=\"/\"><img src=\"/logo.png\" alt=\"Physics Fundamentals\" class=\"h-14 w-auto object-contain\"/></a><ul class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-3\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\"><li><a class=\"relative px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-[14px] transition-all duration-200 flex flex-col items-center justify-center font-semibold\" style=\"color:rgb(148,163,184);background:transparent\" href=\"/\"><span>Home</span></a></li><li><a class=\"relative px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-[14px] transition-all duration-200 flex flex-col items-center justify-center font-semibold\" style=\"color:rgb(148,163,184);background:transparent\" href=\"/about\"><span>About</span></a></li><li><a class=\"relative px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-[14px] transition-all duration-200 flex flex-col items-center justify-center font-semibold\" style=\"color:rgb(148,163,184);background:transparent\" href=\"/blog\"><span>Blog</span></a></li><li><a class=\"relative px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-[14px] transition-all duration-200 flex flex-col items-center justify-center font-semibold\" style=\"color:#ffffff;background:#1e293b\" href=\"/calculators\"><span>Calculators</span><div class=\"absolute bottom-1 w-4 h-0.5 bg-blue-500 rounded-full\"></div></a></li><li><a class=\"relative px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-[14px] transition-all duration-200 flex flex-col items-center justify-center font-semibold\" style=\"color:rgb(148,163,184);background:transparent\" href=\"/simulations\"><span>Simulations</span></a></li><li><a class=\"relative px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-[14px] transition-all duration-200 flex flex-col items-center justify-center font-semibold\" style=\"color:rgb(148,163,184);background:transparent\" href=\"/roadmap\"><span>Roadmap</span></a></li><li><a class=\"relative px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-[14px] transition-all duration-200 flex flex-col items-center justify-center font-semibold\" style=\"color:rgb(148,163,184);background:transparent\" href=\"/contact\"><span>Contact</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-3 shrink-0\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-[#1e293b] active:scale-95\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:600;font-size:14px;color:#60a5fa;padding:8px 18px;border-radius:8px;background:#0f172a;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05)\" href=\"/simulations\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-play fill-blue-400 w-3 h-3 text-blue-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 5a2 2 0 0 1 3.008-1.728l11.997 6.998a2 2 0 0 1 .003 3.458l-12 7A2 2 0 0 1 5 19z\"></path></svg>Play Games</a><a class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-amber-400 active:scale-95 whitespace-nowrap\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#0a0f1e;padding:9px 20px;border-radius:8px;background:#f59e0b\" href=\"/\">Get Early Access</a></div><button id=\"mobile-menu-toggle\" class=\"md:hidden flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-lg text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors bg-white/5 border border-white/10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu w-6 h-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></nav></header><section class=\"mt-[76px] bg-[#0b1221] relative overflow-hidden py-24\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03]\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,1) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,1) 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:40px 40px\"></div><div class=\"max-w-[760px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 text-center relative z-10\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><span class=\"uppercase font-bold tracking-[0.22em] mb-4 block text-blue-400\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-size:11px\">PHYSICS TOOLKIT</span><h1 class=\"text-[clamp(40px,7vw,68px)] leading-[1.05] text-white mb-6\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-instrument-serif);font-weight:400\">Physics Calculators.</h1><p class=\"text-[17px] leading-[1.75] text-slate-400 max-w-[560px] mx-auto mb-14\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Free online calculators for every major physics topic. Enter known variables and instantly receive full solutions with step-by-step working.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-12 gap-y-8\"><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-[28px] font-bold text-white mb-1\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">20+</div><div class=\"text-[12px] font-bold tracking-wider text-slate-500 uppercase\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Calculators</div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-[28px] font-bold text-white mb-1\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">100+</div><div class=\"text-[12px] font-bold tracking-wider text-slate-500 uppercase\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Formulas</div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-[28px] font-bold text-white mb-1\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Free</div><div class=\"text-[12px] font-bold tracking-wider text-slate-500 uppercase\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Access</div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-[28px] font-bold text-white mb-1\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Step-by-step</div><div class=\"text-[12px] font-bold tracking-wider text-slate-500 uppercase\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Solutions</div></div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"bg-white border-b border-slate-200 sticky top-[76px] z-40 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md\"><div class=\"max-w-[1300px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1 overflow-x-auto py-3.5 no-scrollbar\"><button class=\"shrink-0 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-[13px] font-bold tracking-[0.05em] transition-all duration-200 whitespace-nowrap\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);background:#0b1221;color:#ffffff\">All Topics</button><button class=\"shrink-0 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-[13px] font-bold tracking-[0.05em] transition-all duration-200 whitespace-nowrap\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);background:transparent;color:#64748b\">Classical Mechanics</button><button class=\"shrink-0 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-[13px] font-bold tracking-[0.05em] transition-all duration-200 whitespace-nowrap\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);background:transparent;color:#64748b\">Thermodynamics</button><button class=\"shrink-0 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-[13px] font-bold tracking-[0.05em] transition-all duration-200 whitespace-nowrap\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);background:transparent;color:#64748b\">Waves &amp; Optics</button><button class=\"shrink-0 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-[13px] font-bold tracking-[0.05em] transition-all duration-200 whitespace-nowrap\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);background:transparent;color:#64748b\">Electromagnetism</button></div></div></div><section class=\"py-16\"><div class=\"max-w-[1300px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-8\"><h2 class=\"text-[24px] font-bold text-slate-900\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">All Topics<!-- --> Calculators</h2><p class=\"text-[14px] font-semibold text-slate-400\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">20<!-- --> matching tools</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-[#0f172a] rounded-[24px] p-7 flex flex-col border border-[#1e293b] group relative overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.95)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(79,70,229,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%)\"></div><a class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 relative z-10 outline-none\" href=\"/calculators/projectile-motion\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);color:#4f46e5\">Classical Mechanics</span></div><h3 class=\"text-[18px] font-bold text-white mb-3 leading-[1.3]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Projectile Motion Calculator</h3><p class=\"text-[13px] leading-[1.65] text-slate-400 mb-6 flex-1\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Calculate max height, time of flight, range, and current trajectory position given an initial velocity and angle.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-8\"><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-300 border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Range</span><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-300 border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Time</span><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-300 border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Velocity</span><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-300 border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Trajectory</span></div><div class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 py-3.5 rounded-xl text-[14px] font-bold text-white transition-all duration-300 group-active:scale-[0.98] group/btn relative outline-none\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);background:#4f46e5\">Calculate<svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg><div class=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-xl opacity-0 group-hover/btn:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 pointer-events-none\" style=\"box-shadow:0 0 20px #4f46e555\"></div></div></a></div><div class=\"bg-[#0f172a] rounded-[24px] p-7 flex flex-col border border-[#1e293b] group relative overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.95)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(59,130,246,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%)\"></div><a class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 relative z-10 outline-none\" href=\"/calculators/newtons-second-law\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);color:#3b82f6\">Classical Mechanics</span></div><h3 class=\"text-[18px] font-bold text-white mb-3 leading-[1.3]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Newton&#x27;s Second Law Calculator</h3><p class=\"text-[13px] leading-[1.65] text-slate-400 mb-6 flex-1\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Calculate force, mass, or acceleration using F = ma. Supports unit conversions.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-8\"><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-300 border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Force</span><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-300 border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Mass</span><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-300 border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Acceleration</span><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-300 border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Newton</span></div><div class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 py-3.5 rounded-xl text-[14px] font-bold text-white transition-all duration-300 group-active:scale-[0.98] group/btn relative outline-none\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);background:#3b82f6\">Calculate<svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg><div class=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-xl opacity-0 group-hover/btn:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 pointer-events-none\" style=\"box-shadow:0 0 20px #3b82f655\"></div></div></a></div><div class=\"bg-[#0f172a] rounded-[24px] p-7 flex flex-col border border-[#1e293b] group relative overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.95)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(139,92,246,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%)\"></div><a class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 relative z-10 outline-none\" href=\"/calculators/kinetic-energy\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);color:#8b5cf6\">Classical Mechanics</span></div><h3 class=\"text-[18px] font-bold text-white mb-3 leading-[1.3]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Kinetic Energy Calculator</h3><p class=\"text-[13px] leading-[1.65] text-slate-400 mb-6 flex-1\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Compute kinetic energy from mass and velocity, or find the required velocity and mass for a target energy level.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-8\"><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-300 border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Energy</span><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-300 border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Joules</span><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-300 border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Mass</span><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-300 border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Speed</span></div><div class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 py-3.5 rounded-xl text-[14px] font-bold text-white transition-all duration-300 group-active:scale-[0.98] group/btn relative outline-none\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);background:#8b5cf6\">Calculate<svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg><div class=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-xl opacity-0 group-hover/btn:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 pointer-events-none\" style=\"box-shadow:0 0 20px #8b5cf655\"></div></div></a></div><div class=\"bg-[#0f172a] rounded-[24px] p-7 flex flex-col border border-[#1e293b] group relative overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.95)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(245,158,11,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%)\"></div><a class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 relative z-10 outline-none\" href=\"/calculators/ohms-law\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);color:#f59e0b\">Electromagnetism</span></div><h3 class=\"text-[18px] font-bold text-white mb-3 leading-[1.3]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Ohm&#x27;s Law Calculator</h3><p class=\"text-[13px] leading-[1.65] text-slate-400 mb-6 flex-1\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Easily calculate voltage, current, or resistance. Finds missing values based on identical formulas.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-8\"><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-300 border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Voltage</span><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-300 border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Current</span><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-300 border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Resistance</span></div><div class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 py-3.5 rounded-xl text-[14px] font-bold text-white transition-all duration-300 group-active:scale-[0.98] group/btn relative outline-none\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);background:#f59e0b\">Calculate<svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg><div class=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-xl opacity-0 group-hover/btn:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 pointer-events-none\" style=\"box-shadow:0 0 20px #f59e0b55\"></div></div></a></div><div class=\"bg-[#0f172a] rounded-[24px] p-7 flex flex-col border border-[#1e293b] group relative overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.95)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(16,185,129,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%)\"></div><a class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 relative z-10 outline-none\" href=\"/calculators/free-fall\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);color:#10b981\">Classical Mechanics</span></div><h3 class=\"text-[18px] font-bold text-white mb-3 leading-[1.3]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Free Fall Calculator</h3><p class=\"text-[13px] leading-[1.65] text-slate-400 mb-6 flex-1\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Calculates distance, velocity, and time for objects in free fall. Uses Earth&#x27;s standard gravity by default.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-8\"><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-300 border border-slate