\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);color:#6366f1\">Classical Mechanics</span></div><h3 class=\"text-[18px] font-bold text-white mb-3 leading-[1.3]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Escape Velocity Calculator</h3><p class=\"text-[13px] leading-[1.65] text-slate-400 mb-6 flex-1\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Calculate the minimum speed an object needs to escape the gravitational pull of a celestial body.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-8\"><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-300 border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Space</span><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-300 border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Gravity</span><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-300 border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800/30\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Velocity</span></div><div class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 py-3.5 rounded-xl text-[14px] font-bold text-white transition-all duration-300 group-active:scale-[0.98] group/btn relative outline-none\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);background:#6366f1\">Calculate<svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg><div class=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-xl opacity-0 group-hover/btn:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 pointer-events-none\" style=\"box-shadow:0 0 20px #6366f155\"></div></div></a></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-24 bg-white border-t border-slate-200\"><div class=\"max-w-[1000px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\"><span class=\"text-[12px] font-bold tracking-[0.15em] text-blue-500 uppercase block mb-3\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Why Free?</span><h2 class=\"text-[36px] font-bold text-slate-900 mb-5\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Instant physics answers with shown working</h2><p class=\"text-[17px] text-slate-500 max-w-[680px] mx-auto leading-[1.7]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Every calculator on this page reveals the formula and substitution. You won&#x27;t just receive an empty answer; you&#x27;ll see exactly how the physics leads to that answer. No premium paywalls.</p></div><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_1.2fr] gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-start\"><div><h3 class=\"text-[20px] font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">A calculator for every physics topic</h3><p class=\"text-[15px] text-slate-600 leading-[1.8] mb-6\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">From high school mechanics to complex thermodynamics, we&#x27;ve built solvers that handle units natively and map directly to textbook notation.</p><h4 class=\"text-[13px] font-bold tracking-widest text-slate-400 uppercase mb-4 mt-8\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Calculators by topic</h4><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li class=\"flex items-center justify-between border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl px-4 py-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-500\"></span><span class=\"text-[14px] font-bold text-slate-700\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Classical Mechanics</span></div><span class=\"text-[12px] font-semibold text-slate-400\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">11 Calculators</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center justify-between border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl px-4 py-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-orange-500\"></span><span class=\"text-[14px] font-bold text-slate-700\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Thermodynamics</span></div><span class=\"text-[12px] font-semibold text-slate-400\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">2 Calculators</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center justify-between border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl px-4 py-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-pink-500\"></span><span class=\"text-[14px] font-bold text-slate-700\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Waves &amp; Optics</span></div><span class=\"text-[12px] font-semibold text-slate-400\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">4 Calculators</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center justify-between border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl px-4 py-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-indigo-500\"></span><span class=\"text-[14px] font-bold text-slate-700\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Electromagnetism</span></div><span class=\"text-[12px] font-semibold text-slate-400\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">3 Calculators</span></li></ul></div><div><h3 class=\"text-[20px] font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Frequently asked questions</h3><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"border border-slate-200 rounded-[18px] bg-white overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:border-blue-200\" style=\"box-shadow:none\"><button class=\"w-full px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between text-left gap-4 bg-transparent outline-none\"><span class=\"text-[16px] font-bold text-slate-800\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">Are the calculators completely free to use?</span><span class=\"shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-50 flex items-center justify-center\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"transition-transform duration-300 text-blue-500\">